title: the maxx (sam keith) 1-13 on mtvs oddities
description:
This is 7 half hour (22min) episodes of an animated comic strip &#039;The Maxx&#039;. I say animated comic strip because if youve seen the actual comic, the cartoon images are DIRECTLY from the pages. Its awesome, theres still animation in it, but this is Sam Kieth, uncorrupted. 

These episodes aired in the mid-late 90s on Mtv&#039;s Oddities.

These are not high quality, but having said that, they are great quality. You will not be disappointed.

also if you enjoy these, they follow the comic from issue 1-13, the series goes from 1-35, so if you like theres much more story out there, so:

Support your local comic store!
